{"title":"沿着海岸行走","authors":["柳荫"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着海岸行走（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳荫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着海岸行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海折叠的柔情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在涛声之外缠绵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微饧的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹动花发的忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，你漫长的生命线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个温暖的港湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都拥抱着日日夜夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些渔夫那些水手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些沉默的劳动者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在热爱的土地上歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着海岸行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸的排浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吟诵不朽的诗章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙滩松软得像绒毯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是母亲辽远的胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，你的黄金曲线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描绘沉积的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精美的风景如歌如画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹性的舌尖赞美天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮声有节奏地涨落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手捧出一轮鲜红的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打捞沉船的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打捞沉船的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像风从我身边走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的牙齿很白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的面孔很黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们沉默着没有语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台风已经远去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛的罪恶使大海开满花圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的灵魂遨游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆断裂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使他们执着香烟的手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在苦难中冒烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打捞沉船的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像风从我身边掠过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不发一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟头一闪一亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸孔岩石般粗糙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我能感知他们的痛苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能看到他们心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立着大山一样不倒的信念"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}